rall morphology of the postcranial skeleton of Hyopsodus indicates a nimble, fast moving animal that likely lived in burrows. This would be compatible with terrestrial echolocation used by the animal to investigate subterranean habitat and/or to minimize predation during nocturnal exploration of the environment.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Orliac, Maeva J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Argot, Christine", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gilissen, Emmanuel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Goswami, Anjali", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/55ac86811395c8d2a114217900c404ad", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/72ecc8010d0cdba7b602bceaabd9543f375020a2dc4bc17f196b1bf01e64df9a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/JUWMW6QM", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/JUWMW6QM", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/ecfe66b99ee689b2f1e5bbb81226972b!/b7-2417", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "2", "pages": "e30000", "title": "PLoS ONE", "volume": "7"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/55ac86811395c8d2a114217900c404ad"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:JUWMW6QM"}, {"identifier": "10.1371/j